# Paper Knowledge Loader Skill Equivalent

- Use this workflow when a persona should learn from an academic paper or university research output.
- Prefer the primary paper sections: abstract, methods, evaluation, appendices, and linked technical assets.
- Create a dedicated paper persona for first-level skills extracted from that work.
- Store local knowledge bundles under `.ai/paper-imports/<paper-slug>/`.
- Keep memories, technical notes, and transferable skill packs separate.
- Make archivist personas track and index these bundles rather than own the paper skills.
- Keep coverage aligned with Copilot and Claude Code and record support in `SUPPORTED.md`.
